resources.string: This app was built to test the Tiden US Sandbox Verify service for the front and back of a license. To use without MiSnap: Insert Credentials in the corresponding fields. Press the "Test Tiden Credentials" Button. Upon Receiving Token Confirmation From the Server on the following Activity, Press the red action button at the bottom of the screen. This will send a hardcoded base64 image to the server and display the Mobile Verify JSON results. To use with MiSnap: Press the "Invoke MiSnap Capture" Button to start the MiSnap capture. Capture the front and back of a US license with the corresponding Buttons. Enter your US Tiden Sandbox Credentials in the below fields after the license is captured. Press the "Test Tiden Credentials" Button and proceed with the workflow. This will replace the base64 image from memory with whatever image you captured with MiSnap. Thanks
